product_description: Krishna Creations is a brand started by a 73 year old grandma, who loves the idea of looking good. The brand is a small business right now, which surely looks at growing multifold and making women feel happier about their look by simple accessories. We are sure you must have heard your grandmothers or mothers tell you, “You have so many clothes, just wear them differently to have a new look.” Often we miss the value that an accessory could add to our look. Krishna Creations started with a vision and mission to help women wear the same outfit with a different look. As our grandma says, “Just change the accessories and no one will know you wore the same dress.” Each belt is made with love, supervised by our Chief Supervisor, our grandma!
